CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 11, 1945, pg. 13, reads: "The Oldest - Oliver Jones, oldest living member of the Frogs, and little Herman Scott, pose. L. to r.: Misses Jean Stanton and Audrey Moore on one side; Gladys Grisby and Peggy Moore on the other. - All Photos By Harris."
TitMainTitle: Jean Stanton, Audrey Moore (Daniels), Oliver Jones, Gladys Grisby, Margaret Moore (Brown), and Herman Scott in front, in South Park lodge for FROGS picnic
